      "role": "user",
      "content": "i keep looking at the stars or just looking out the window at night and everything just feels so incredibly empty. like, there's no grand design, no purpose, just a bunch of atoms drifting around until they stop. it’s hard to see any point in even trying anymore when the end result is just total nothingness.",
